title: Junortoun Flora
description: Spring 2016 collection of local flora after unusually high rainfall over the winter months around the Somerset Rd area, Junortoun, Victoria.

_display.description_html: Spring 2016 collection of local flora after unusually high rainfall over the winter months around the Somerset Rd area, Junortoun, Victoria.
